title: Rare Hits of The 80s Vol. 32
description:
Yet another mix of synth and new wave rarities from the 80z! Possibly the last one though. Please keep seeding these mixes for the others to explore this other side of the 80z. If you'd like me to torrent a full LP of any of these obscure bands, send me a request by e-mail to danieldking at gmail dot com. [of course if the band was not a one-single-wonder!]
